Notes on the Competition Draw Manager:
######################################

Actors:
    Player
    Organiser

Actions:
    Register_For_Event
    Withdraw_From_Event, reason hurt, unfit, beaten in a round
    Participate_In_Event, play the actual game

    Publish_Results
    Start_Event
    End_Event
    Enter_Result
    Clear_Result
    Edit_Result
    Add_Handicap
    Find_Player
    Find_Team
    Create_Team
    Create_Competition, singles, doubles, handycap, plate

    Create_List(Type)
    Manage_Team_List
    Manage_Player_List
    Manage_Competition_List




